IN THE WORLD OF FOOTBALL, an image is everything because, aside from what players do on the field, their appearance is always a talking point. One thing that always makes people's tongues wag is their various and unique hairstyles. Whether the hair is in good condition or in a state of disarray, it always draws some interest and attention.And Brazil's and PSG's Neymar has taken it to a new level with his new hairdo. The 29-year-old walked out of the hairdresser with blond dreadlock-style plaits, which sparked a social media frenzy among fans.  Neymar made headlines earlier this year when he dyed his hair pink before a PSG match against Montpellier.  Some of nis umique hairstyles. 